{"tid":2362042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地智庫稱美軍戰略無人偵察機周末飛近廣東及福建","createTime":"2021-01-11T07:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T07:35:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa1ba636cdba7c369bb82560f525c8e3b3ddfaf","tid":2362042,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569750-20210111.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569750-20210111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=e7e3e240\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569750-20210111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=52977c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569750-20210111.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍戰略無人偵察機，上星期六在南海上空飛行，一度飛近廣東及福建沿岸。<br />\n<br />\n北京大學「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」在社交網站，公布美軍MQ-4C戰略無人偵察機的飛行路線，無人機由巴士海峽進入南海，飛抵廣東及福建交界後返航。據平台統計，今次是同款的無人機在今個月以來，第三次現身南海。<br />\n<br />\nMQ-4C無人機是美國海軍最先進的水面監控平台之一，機上配備完善的探測設備，可以大範圍監視海上目標，最遠可以飛行超過1萬5千公里，最長飛行時間為30小時。"},{"pid":"b2425018b4c63d7936d02eab51000338b196e022","tid":2362042,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"肉醬意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}